Go,
Henry;
you
must
learn
to
take
your
share
of
the
bitter
of
life
with
all
of
Adam's
race
that
have
gone
before
or
will
come
after
you.
Your
destiny
can
be
no
exception
to
the
common
lot;
be
grateful
that
your
love
is
overlooked
thus
early,
before
it
can
claim
any
affinity
to
passion.
An
