of
envy,
suffice
to
express
what
you
feel.
Jealousy
hot
as
the
sun
above
the
line,
rage
destructive
as
the
tropic
storm,
the
clime
of
your
sensations
ignores
as
yet.
"I
took
my
usual
seat
at
the
desk,
quite
in
my
usual
way.
I
am
blessed
in
that
power
to
cover
all
inward
