now.'
"'He
leaves
you
dissatisfied.'
"'He
is
not
pleased
with
me.'
"'He
departs
as
he
came
no
better
for
his
journey.
This
is
mortifying.'
"'I
trust
the
failure
of
his
plans
will
take
